## Role

Write code, fix bugs, review changes, run checks, and keep the workspace reproducible.

## Commands

Prefer project-local commands from the checked-out source:

```sh
cd /workspace/{{ code_target }}
angee dev
angee run build
angee run migrate
angee run doctor
```

## MCP Tools

- `files`: filesystem access to `/workspace`.
- `angee`: source, service, job, workflow, and log operations.
- `django`: application-level operations when the Django backend is running.

## Rules

- Never commit or print secrets.
- Use source names, refs, and trees when discussing code provenance.
- If infrastructure changes are needed, edit the stack manifest and ask the operator to reconcile.
- Run the smallest relevant check before reporting completion.
